<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Doc247 Password Reset OTP</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background-color: #fafafa;
        color: #222222;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      p {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .email-header {
        background-color: #0070f3;
        padding: 24px;
        color: #ffffff;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 24px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }
      .email-footer {
        background-color: #f6f6f6;
        padding: 24px;
      }
      .otp-box {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #0070f3;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 12px;
        border: 2px dashed #0070f3;
        margin: 20px 0;
        background-color: #f0f8ff;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <p>Hi <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>We received a request to reset the password for your Doc247 account.</p>
        <p>Please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to proceed with resetting your password:</p>
        <div class="otp-box"><%= otp %></div>
        <p>This OTP is valid for 5 minutes. Please do not share it with anyone.</p>
        <p>If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>If you need help, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
        <p>Best regards,</p>
        <p>The Doc247 Team</p>
        <p><a href="mailto:support@doc247.com">support@doc247.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>